dc_description_s: This data represents zoning in Lafayette County, Wisconsin in 2020. The following features are incuded: GENERAL and MUNICIPAL_ZONING. [Participating towns include: Argyle, Belmont, Elk Grove, Fayette, Gratiot, Kendall, Lamont, Monticello, Shullsburg, Wayne, & Wiota.Zoning Districts are as follows:A-1 Working Lands Initiative (Farmland Preservation Eligibility)A-2 Ag LandsRR Rural ResidentialR-1 Single Family ResidentialR-2 Multi Family Residential (Condo)R-3 Mobile Home Park or Multi Unit ResidentialB-1 Rural BusinessC-1 Commercial BusinessM-1 Light IndustrialM-2 Heavy IndustrialCFR Conservation, Forestry, and Recreation]
